name: Loading out
description:
Hey, I'm Daol and I'm making a big step today. I'm leaving my small hometown to move to Denmark. Could you help me load my stuff to my truck? I need to visit my family members to pick up everything.

CONTROLS

W-A-S-D, space bar, up-down-left-right, mouse, mouse wheel

The controls change based on the minigame you are playing. You'll figure it out!
